speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add Brussels sprouts, salt and pepper and cook <b>4-6 min\/100°C\/\/speed <b> or until cooked to your preference."},{"content":"To serve, place Brussels sprouts and lime crumb together in a serving bowl and toss gently to combine."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This is a great side dish to serve with roasted potatoes and your choice of meat or fish.","To enjoy this dish as leftovers the next day, leave the lime crumb and Brussels sprouts separate. Store the Brussels sprouts in the refrigerator and the lime crumb at room temperature. Reheat Brussels sprouts the following day and combine with lime crumb just before serving.","To make this dish gluten free, use gluten free bread. Always read the labels of your products to ensure no wheat or gluten has been used as part of the production process.","<strong>Recipe for one: <\/strong>Reduce all ingredients, except water, by half. Leave the water at 1 tbsp in step 6 and proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","20m","2 portions"]}